  ${
    $d U a b $.  $d R a b $.  $d B a b $.  $d Z a b $.
    drngnidl.b $e |- B = ( Base ` R ) $.
    drngnidl.z $e |- Z = ( 0g ` R ) $.
    drngnidl.u $e |- U = ( LIdeal ` R ) $.
